[I] A DNS resolver module

[T] Net::DNS is a DNS resolver implemented in Perl. It allows the
[T] programmer to perform nearly any type of DNS query from a Perl
[T] script.

[U] https://www.net-dns.org/

[A] Olaf Kolkman <olaf@net-dns.org>
